  pure-ftpd-1.0.20.ebuild:
  Added privilege separation option to configure.

  01 Sep 2004; Gustavo Felisberto <humpback@gentoo.org>;
  pure-ftpd-1.0.20.ebuild:
  Updated username lenght limit from 32 to 127, see bug #62472 for details.

